<p class=MsoNormal align=center style='text-align:center'><span
style='font-size:22.0pt;font-family:"宋体";color:white'>红中宝麻将</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>一、游戏人数</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>4</span><span
style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>人</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>二、麻将牌数</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>筒字：<span
lang=EN-US>1~9X4=36</span>张；条字：<span lang=EN-US>1~9X4=36</span>张；万字：<span
lang=EN-US>1~9X4=36</span>张；共<span lang=EN-US>108</span>张。</span></p>

<p style='margin:0cm;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:justify;text-justify:
inter-ideograph;line-height:150%'><span style='font-size:10.5pt;
line-height:150%;font-family:"宋体";color:white'>宝牌：中，<span lang=EN-US>4</span>张。总计<span
lang=EN-US>112</span>张。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><b><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>三、出牌规则</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>打牌时不能吃牌，只能碰杠。胡牌时，其他的牌型胡牌都必须要自摸。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>3.1<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>庄家规则</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>第一局由系统抛出的骰子数决定出庄家，之后由上一圈的胡牌者担任庄家。和局后庄家继续坐庄。闲家胡牌后庄家下庄，下盘由胡牌家做庄。流局后庄家继续做庄。坐庄没有翻倍。庄家拥有第一轮的出牌权。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>约战特殊要求：开房者如果参与游戏，则第一局开房者是庄家。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>3.2<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>红中宝牌规则</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>红中可以代替任意牌进行游戏；红中自己可以进行碰杠，但无加分。红中宝牌共有<span
lang=EN-US>4</span>个。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>3.3<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>马牌规则</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>i.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>普通奖码</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>马牌不参与摸牌，需要留码牌<span
lang=EN-US>+2</span>张牌，不给摸。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>最后自摸者进行奖码（<span
lang=EN-US>1,5,9</span>，红中，则中码）。如自摸牌型中没红中加奖多两个码。不用管庄家是谁，和风位。任何一个方位的玩家，都是以：<span
lang=EN-US>1,5,9</span>，红中，则算中码。</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>ii.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>一码必中</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>摸到最后剩下一张牌，不能摸。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>最后自摸者进行奖码，必中；摸中的码牌数字是多少，就算中了多少头码；例如摸到<span
lang=EN-US>5</span>万，则算中<span lang=EN-US>5</span>头码。红中则奖励<span lang=EN-US>10</span>头。</span></p>

<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Wingdings'>l<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;
</span></span><b><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>分数算法</span></b></p>

<p class=MsoNormal><span lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>1</span><span
style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>分<span lang=EN-US>=</span>房间设定的底分。</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>明杠</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:0cm'><span
style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>直杠：<span lang=EN-US>3</span>分，放杠者出<span
lang=EN-US>3</span>分；自己有暗刻，碰别人打出的一张相同的牌开杠。</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:0cm'><span
style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>面下杠：<span lang=EN-US>1</span>分，所有玩家出<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>分；自己抓进一张与碰的明刻相同的牌开杠。 </span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>2.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>暗杠：<span
lang=EN-US>2</span>分，所有玩家出<span lang=EN-US>2</span>分；在打牌过程中自己摸得<span
lang=EN-US>4</span>张一样的牌，若开杠则为暗杠。</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>3.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>抢杠胡：开明杠被抢的玩家，全包，其他<span
lang=EN-US>2</span>家的分数也是由他出；</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:0cm'><span
style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>如果一家听胡的牌正好是其它家正在开面下杠的牌，则称作抢杠胡。</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:0cm'><span
style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>玩家抢杠时将不能抢自己所打的牌，如：自己打出一张三条，有人杠，此时将无法对其进行抢杠操作。
</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>4.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>自摸：<span
lang=EN-US>2</span>分；没有吃、碰、明杠的胡牌。</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>5.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>码牌：只算房间底分，明杠和暗杠不计算在码中；多少个码，就算多少倍底分分数。</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:0cm'><span
style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>如玩一码必中；<span lang=EN-US>A</span>玩家自摸<span
lang=EN-US>+1</span>个暗杠，且中了<span lang=EN-US>4</span>个码。<span lang=EN-US>B</span>玩家有<span
lang=EN-US>1</span>个暗杠；<span lang=EN-US>C</span>玩家有一个直杠（<span lang=EN-US>A</span>玩家放的杠），<span
lang=EN-US>D</span>玩家有一个面下杠。</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:0cm'><span
style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>则：</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:0cm'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>B</span><span
style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>玩家输：<span lang=EN-US>2</span>（<span
lang=EN-US>A</span>自摸）<span lang=EN-US>+2</span>（<span lang=EN-US>A</span>暗杠）<span
lang=EN-US>+4</span>（<span lang=EN-US>A4</span>个码）<span lang=EN-US>+1</span>（<span
lang=EN-US>D</span>面下杠）<span lang=EN-US>-6</span>（<span lang=EN-US>B</span>自己暗杠）<span
lang=EN-US>=3</span>；</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:0cm'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>C</span><span
style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>玩家输：<span lang=EN-US>2</span>（<span
lang=EN-US>A</span>自摸）<span lang=EN-US>+2</span>（<span lang=EN-US>A</span>暗杠）<span
lang=EN-US>+4</span>（<span lang=EN-US>A4</span>个码）<span lang=EN-US>+2</span>（<span
lang=EN-US>B</span>暗杠）<span lang=EN-US>+1</span>（<span lang=EN-US>D</span>玩家面下杠）<span
lang=EN-US>-3</span>（直杠<span lang=EN-US>A</span>的）<span lang=EN-US>=8</span>；</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:0cm'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>D</span><span
style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>玩家输：<span lang=EN-US>2</span>（<span
lang=EN-US>A</span>自摸）<span lang=EN-US>+2</span>（<span lang=EN-US>A</span>暗杠）<span
lang=EN-US>+4</span>（<span lang=EN-US>A4</span>个码）<span lang=EN-US>+2</span>（<span
lang=EN-US>B</span>暗杠）<span lang=EN-US>-3</span>（面下杠）<span lang=EN-US>=7</span>；</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:0cm'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>A</span><span
style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>玩家赢：（<span lang=EN-US>2</span>自摸<span
lang=EN-US>+4</span>码牌<span lang=EN-US>+2</span>暗杠）<span lang=EN-US>*3</span>（<span
lang=EN-US>3</span>家）<span lang=EN-US>-2</span>暗杠（<span lang=EN-US>B</span>）<span
lang=EN-US>-3</span>（直杠给<span lang=EN-US>C</span>）<span lang=EN-US>-1</span>（<span
lang=EN-US>D</span>的面下杠）<span lang=EN-US>=24-6=18</span>；</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:0cm'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>18=A+B+C</span><span
style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>（<span lang=EN-US>ABC</span>所输的），验证正确。<span
lang=EN-US>.</span></span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:21.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:Wingdings'>l<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>特殊说明：</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>1.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>明杠和暗杠，最后自己没自摸或牌局流局，分数依旧有效。</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>2.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>没一炮多响，没其他胡牌类型。</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>3.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>有过手胡。（自己放弃的胡，别人打出来不能胡）。但没有过手碰（自己打的，别人打也可以碰）。</span></p>

<p class=MsoListParagraph style='margin-left:42.0pt;text-indent:-21.0pt'><span
lang=EN-US style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>4.<span style='font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span><span style='font-family:"宋体";color:white'>手里有刻子，别人打出来，可碰可杠。只选择了碰，则以后都不提示杠这个牌了。</span></p>

